This code is part of a project where a haptic device (the GeoMagc Phantom) and a human jointly colaborate to create a painting.
A paintbrush was mounted in place of the pen and a white sheet of paper. More information in this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A96bW_4CtQc.

Contributors: Kim Baraka, Su Baykal, Yeliz Karadayi and Robert Zacharias.
